</title><link>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/4701/a-way-to-split-layout-always-32/?comment=4759#comment-4759</link><description>You can sort of get what he's looking for with the IPC interface, but not exactly due to rounding. Limited to 200 characters, but I explained it in a question I asked (https://faq.i3wm.org/question/3882/px-vs-ppt-for-resize/). You won't be able to get an exact (e.g. 60/40) size split.</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Oct 2014 20:53:29 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/4701/a-way-to-split-layout-always-32/?comment=4759#comment-4759</guid></item></channel></rss>